# Component split gate

**Kit:** `docs/agent-playbook/README.md`  
**Universal:** `docs/agent-playbook/core/file-split-policy.md`  
**React:** `docs/agent-playbook/frameworks/react.md`  
**Backlog:** `docs/project/restructure-plan.md`

## Lint caps

- File: **200** code lines · Function: **60** · Complexity: **15**
- At **150** code lines: extract before growing.

## Buckets (React)

| Layer | Location |
| ----- | -------- |
| Render | `components/<domain>/*.tsx` |
| Domain hook | `components/<domain>/use*.ts` |
| Shared hook | `hooks/use*.ts` |
| Provider | `context/use*Controller.ts` |
| Pure logic | `lib/` — no JSX |

## Domain folders

`code/` · `explorer/` · `graph/` · `nodes/` · `simulation/` · `ui/`

Root `components/*.tsx` = shell composers only.

## Split order

1. `lib/` → 2. hook/controller → 3. child components → 4. thin parent

No `.html` in React — extract child `.tsx`.
